### Get all restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific restaurant by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/id/3

### Get a specific restaurant by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/name/Sushi%20Zen

### Get opens restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/open

### Get restaurants by rate
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/rate/4

### Post a new restaurant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5,
  "name": "Ifeanyi's Diner",
  "foodType": "Italian",
  "address": "123 Main St, Anytown",
  "openHour": "08:00",
  "closeHour": "22:00",
  "rate": 4

}

### Update an existing restaurant
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/id/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5,
  "name": "Ifeanyi's Diner",
  "foodType": "African",
  "address": "123 Main St, Anytown",
  "openHour": "08:00",
  "closeHour": "22:00",
  "rate": 4
}

### Delete a restaurant by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/restaurant/id/1
Content-Type: application/json

